&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Senior Emergency Nurse Practitioner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced Emergency Nurse Practitioner who is committed to working as part of our Urgent Care Team delivering an excellent, caring service to our patients. We are currently in the process of transitioning our service from an Urgent Care Centre to a nationally mandated Urgent Treatment Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have a multidisciplinary workforce made up primarily of Nurse Clinicians, Emergency Nurse Practitioners trained in both Adult and Paediatric disciplines and Doctors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main patient groups are Patients with Minor Injury and Minor illness. The Practitioners/Clinicians manage these Patients who present to the Urgent Care Centre with an undifferentiated diagnosis through a process of assessment, formulation of a clinical management plan and on to discharge or transfer for definitive care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Are you an experienced Nurse looking for a new challenge? Do you have?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significant experience as an Emergency Nurse Practitioner (Adult or Paediatric)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in assessment of patients with Minor illness/injury&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for delivering high quality patient care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding communication and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to deliver safe, effective and compassionate care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A commitment to continual personal and professional development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to make a difference to people’s lives by becoming a dedicated and compassionate nurse practitioner, then come and be part of one of our friendly multi-disciplinary teams. We offer a challenging and rewarding experience, striving for excellence in patient safety, quality and continuous improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position is full time worked over a 7 day shift pattern 365 days a Year&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
